ungsprozesse betrachtet wird, wird in den Beiträgen dieses Bandes nach der Grammatikalisierung der Wortarten selbst (in Sprachsystem und Spracherwerb) gefragt.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 17. Dez 2021) 0aGrammar, Comparative and general. 0aLinguistics. 4aSprachwandel. 4aWortart. 7aLANGUAGE ARTS & DISCIPLINES / Grammar & Punctuation.2bisacsh1 aBehrens, Heike, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aEisenberg, Peter, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFrevel, Claudia, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHimmelmann, Nikolaus, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKnobloch, Clemens, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKnobloch, Clemens, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aLehmann, Christian, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRedder, Angelika, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSchaeder, Burkhard, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aVogel, Petra M., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aÁgel, Vilmos, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Linguistics and Semiotics 2000 - 2014z9783110636970oZDB-23-DLS08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK GESAMTPAKET / COMPLETE PACKAGE 2008z9783110212129oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PAKET LINGUISTIK UND LITERATURWISSENSCHAFT  2008z9783110209457oZDB-23-DGA0 cprintz978311018411240uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311020209040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110202090423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110202090/original  aEBA_BA